data.description: Introducing a charming 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2 and a half bath house located in the sought-after Wrightwood neighborhood. Long time owner, this lovely home boasts hardwood floors throughout, adding a touch of elegance to its interior. The updated kitchen is sure to impress, offering modern appliances and ample space for culinary endeavors. The property features a partially finished basement, providing additional living or storage space to suit your needs. With many windows strategically placed throughout, the house is flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Convenient 2-car garage is available, ensuring secure parking and extra storage options. The home's exterior is adorned with all-brick construction, adding to its durability and timeless appeal. Situated in a prime location, this property offers easy access to Midway Airport and nearby Metra stations, making commuting a breeze.
